OL,3,CInquest finds no fault in medical care
OL,4,Cafter 17-year-old's death in Jersey.
OL,6,FAn inquest into the cause of Daisy
OL,7,FStephenson's death has found she died
OL,8,Ffrom SUDEP: Sudden Unexpected Death in
OL,9,FEpilepsy.
OL,11,FThe Coroner concluded that she was
OL,12,Fhaving regular seizures in the months
OL,13,Fbefore her death in May 2023, despite
OL,14,Fthe best efforts of her parents and
OL,15,Fthe work of clinicians in Jeresy,
OL,16,FSouthampton and Great Ormond Street.
