OL,3,CInquest finds no fault in medical care
OL,4,Cafter 17-year-old's death in Jersey.
OL,6,FDaisy's epilepsy was severe and
OL,7,Fresistant to drugs. Doctors tried
OL,8,Faround a dozen different medications
OL,9,Fto manage her condition and the option
OL,10,Fof surgery was also explored.
OL,12,FHer parents, Claire and Warren
OL,13,FStephenson, told the hearing that they
OL,14,Fbelieved her condition was poorly
OL,15,Fmanaged and that her death 'could have
OL,16,Fbeen avoided'. They're calling for
OL,17,Fmore support and awareness for those
OL,18,Fwho have the condition on island.
