OL,3,CInquest finds no fault in medical care
OL,4,Cafter 17-year-old's death in Jersey.
OL,6,FThe Charity Epilepsy Action say: "It
OL,7,Fcan affect anyone, at any stage of
OL,8,Ftheir life. So it's really important
OL,9,Fpeople understand just how serious
OL,10,Fepilepsy can be.
OL,12,F"Around a thousand people with
OL,13,Fepilepsy die every year and and in
OL,14,Faround 500 of those cases, it's often
OL,15,Funexpected. It's not clear what the
OL,16,Fcause is."
