OL,3,CInquest finds no fault in medical care
OL,4,Cafter 17-year-old's death in Jersey.
OL,6,FJersey signed up to a national
OL,7,Fprogramme intended to improve the
OL,8,Fquality of care for children and young
OL,9,Fpeople with epilepsy in the year after
OL,10,FDaisy's death.
OL,12,FIt's known as the Epilepsy12 audit, a
OL,13,FUK-wide scheme that measures how well
OL,14,Fepilepsy services are being delivered.
